    <item>
      <title>电动汽车领导者挪威不会跟随欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/ev-leader-norway-won-t-follow-eu-on-chinese-electric-car-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威财政部长特里格夫·斯拉格斯沃尔德·维杜姆 (Trygve Slagsvold Vedum) 表示，挪威是插电式汽车普及的先驱者，不会加入欧盟对中国电动汽车提高关税的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/ev-leader-norway-won-t-follow-eu-on-chinese-electric-car-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 13:19:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
